{"tid":1033356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗17億元天橋 路署未審批先招標","createTime":"2019-02-23T05:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T14:52:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81191c6d359aa5b4e64a7fd76cbc833a4f8f5e55","tid":1033356,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190223/20619062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190223%2F20619062&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1HNo2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=9b471b2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190223%2F20619062&h=2efd3d25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190223/20619062</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗17億元天橋 路署未審批先招標<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190223/large/18737081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190223%2Flarge%2F18737081.jpg&h=13d1b59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】路政署早前向立法會財委會申請超過17億元撥款，在元朗興建天價行人天橋（圖），在立法會強烈反對下抽起撥款申請後，路政署昨突然為天橋招標，料7月展開工程，更聘請曾於多項政府大型工程中屢爆醜聞的奧雅納工程顧問有限公司擔任設計和監督。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顧問奧雅納劣迹斑斑<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員鄺俊宇批評，路政署堅持聘用劣迹斑斑的顧問公司，令公眾有極差觀感，要求交代為何未未審批先招標。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，奧雅納曾出任政府多項大型基建的顧問公司，包括港珠澳大橋、深圳灣公路大橋、廣深港高鐵香港段，但均被揭出現不同工程問題，包括港珠澳大橋被揭發有大量工程紀錄缺失；深圳灣公路大橋有鋼纜近日疑因銹蝕而折斷；高鐵則曾因計算錯誤，去年測試時，列車發生出軌事故。<br />\n<br />\n路政署主要工程管理處副處長駱劍華回應指，政府昨進行同步招標的動作，邀請投標者提出更具成本效益的建造方法和創新建議，是希望減低建造成本。<br />\n<br />\n駱劍華又指7月只是預期動工日期，該署會適時再向財委會申請撥款。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n楊岳橋關鍵一票 西九職位撥款否決<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌： 將愛化作力氣 郭婞淳"},{"pid":"47c1afaba7af9288e87ccd7d7c30731299fdf9d7","tid":1033356,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48129bb5d8f7a093aa4703e5ae4ca1a35c1ccd2f","tid":1033356,"uid":229183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b64767f0c3447cb1864523ecb252eb14fe8bdff3","tid":1033356,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"Parallel tendering<br />\n<br />\n成日都做架啦<br />\n<br />\n你立法會唔批funding，就算佢有標返，都冇得簽約開工"},{"pid":"769537930d1aa7c57f5cb2fa7e00af04ccca5d54","tid":1033356,"uid":106848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"又係奧雅納，正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe34b7089162765c0a083dce1015cd3ae122d6f","tid":1033356,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64767f0c3447cb1864523ecb252eb14fe8bdff3","tid":1033356,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"Parallel tendering<br />\n<br />\n成日都做架啦<br />\n<br />\n你立法會唔批funding，就算佢有標返，都冇得簽約開工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"你定啦<br />\n呢班人會唔批？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saPmbML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaPmbML.jpg&h=33134711&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e08a9a24f6376fe85a82d7e1ee632a5ba70ad81","tid":1033356,"uid":5546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"不意外"},{"pid":"778be4e04f33f55bb75e594073959df4001d8171","tid":1033356,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike"